export const getConditionalText = (stateId) => {
  switch (stateId) {
    case 'LA':
    case 'ME':
    case 'OH':
      return 'If partners are non-residents';
    case 'NH':
      return 'Over $50k income';
    case 'UT':
      return 'If partners are corporate or non-residents';
    default:
      return 'See detailed notes for specific criteria';
  }
};
